description: Hey Papis....I hope some of you out there were able to catch us at our favorite club again. If not dont worry thats what the site is for. We had a blast and were welcomed with open arms and legs...LOL. We had many fans in there and the whole club was jumpin. We had many people participating in our activities. Wait till u guys see the PAPIs we took home...there was a lot of love in the air and they put on a show for us all...enjoy PAPIs.
title: Cock Shots
